1
00:00:02,015 --> 00:00:06,030
[One year ago]

2
00:00:08,836 --> 00:00:13,720
Well, we're all around the same age,
with similar goals, right?

3
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,602
We should have each other's backs.

4
00:00:15,602 --> 00:00:18,189
Who knows? We might be friends after the camp.

5
00:00:18,189 --> 00:00:20,782
This isn't a playground.

6
00:00:20,782 --> 00:00:23,962
Have each other's backs?
We're not here to make friends.

7
00:00:25,349 --> 00:00:27,962
Of course debuting is our priority.

8
00:00:27,962 --> 00:00:30,682
Let's all make it so that we can be friends.

9
00:00:30,682 --> 00:00:33,635
Team A, get ready for the stage.

10
00:00:38,909 --> 00:00:41,122
I want to be friends with you.

11
00:00:41,122 --> 00:00:43,222
Wish you luck.

12
00:00:45,069 --> 00:00:46,817
Good luck.

13
00:01:26,187 --> 00:01:27,952
Are you all right?

14
00:01:32,981 --> 00:01:36,859
No, you're not. You're burning hot.

15
00:01:36,859 --> 00:01:38,792
I'm fine.

16
00:01:38,792 --> 00:01:40,711
I'm just cold.

17
00:01:44,521 --> 00:01:46,719
What are you doing?

18
00:01:46,719 --> 00:01:48,352
Trust me.

19
00:01:48,352 --> 00:01:50,452
Just stay like this for a second.

20
00:02:00,772 --> 00:02:02,872
What's with these two?

21
00:02:08,885 --> 00:02:11,705
Stay still. This is a nice shot.

22
00:02:11,705 --> 00:02:13,905
No, no, stay there.

23
00:02:13,905 --> 00:02:16,445
Come on, take the shot. This is realism.

24
00:02:16,445 --> 00:02:19,312
We can make something out of this.

25
00:02:25,519 --> 00:02:30,565
Now, it's time to announce the rankings
for the next stage.

26
00:02:30,565 --> 00:02:35,400
Everyone gave their best
performances during the past missions.

27
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:37,945
Sadly, the trainees with the lowest ranking,

28
00:02:37,945 --> 00:02:41,999
according to the votes, will be eradicated.

29
00:02:41,999 --> 00:02:47,299
Now, we will proceed
with the first round of announcements.

30
00:02:52,445 --> 00:02:53,992
Hey, Soo An...

31
00:02:53,992 --> 00:02:56,425
Let's make our debut.

32
00:03:31,695 --> 00:03:36,141
If I offer to take you home,
I know you'll say no.

33
00:03:36,141 --> 00:03:40,739
But if I let you go home on your own,
well, I'd worry for your safety.

34
00:03:42,685 --> 00:03:44,985
Which do you prefer?

35
00:03:44,985 --> 00:03:46,912
Yoon Soo An?

36
00:03:47,811 --> 00:03:50,312
You can go ahead.

37
00:03:50,312 --> 00:03:53,325
- Huh?
- You can go home.

38
00:03:55,952 --> 00:03:58,052
Hey, are you okay?

39
00:04:18,172 --> 00:04:21,397
Anyway, it's nice to see you here.

40
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,839
If you want to touch my hand,

41
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:28,183
you should ask me first.

42
00:04:28,183 --> 00:04:30,052
Is this my fault?

43
00:04:30,052 --> 00:04:32,368
- Huh?
- So I've got to say sorry?

44
00:04:32,368 --> 00:04:33,719
No, I never said that.

45
00:04:33,719 --> 00:04:35,305
Then why are you talking like that?

46
00:04:35,305 --> 00:04:37,865
Why are you acting like I'm being sensitive?

47
00:04:37,865 --> 00:04:41,239
What do you want me to do now?

48
00:04:41,239 --> 00:04:43,223
Let's just be...

49
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:45,897
classmates.

50
00:04:46,985 --> 00:04:51,265
Even now he's out here defending
some Thai guy who just rolled in,

51
00:04:51,265 --> 00:04:52,712
or what,

52
00:04:52,712 --> 00:04:54,625
is Shin Jae Min into him?

53
00:04:54,625 --> 00:04:57,359
Say what you want about me

54
00:04:57,359 --> 00:04:59,524
but leave Khun out of it.

55
00:05:01,725 --> 00:05:03,825
Khun!

56
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:07,979
Want to get some ice cream?

57
00:05:17,965 --> 00:05:20,385
Don't let it get to you.

58
00:05:20,385 --> 00:05:21,865
Such jerks.

59
00:05:21,865 --> 00:05:23,817
They're hammered.

60
00:05:28,245 --> 00:05:30,765
Do you think so too?

61
00:05:30,765 --> 00:05:32,291
What?

62
00:05:33,618 --> 00:05:36,892
That I have tapped in out of nowhere.

63
00:05:36,892 --> 00:05:39,192
No, of course not.

64
00:05:42,012 --> 00:05:44,845
Okay. Got it.

65
00:05:46,865 --> 00:05:48,887
Honestly, I...

66
00:05:50,712 --> 00:05:52,617
I just...

67
00:05:55,981 --> 00:05:57,636
Never mind.

68
00:05:58,432 --> 00:06:00,352
See you tomorrow in class.

69
00:06:00,945 --> 00:06:02,532
You're coming, right?

70
00:06:07,359 --> 00:06:10,139
Good luck, classmate.

71
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:30,972
I knew you drank too much.

72
00:06:36,799 --> 00:06:39,264
I guess you were nervous.

73
00:07:23,359 --> 00:07:26,085
Could you get me some orange juice?

74
00:07:41,932 --> 00:07:43,261
Business.

75
00:07:43,261 --> 00:07:44,972
You used me to get ahead and I did the same,

76
00:07:44,972 --> 00:07:46,809
and you already made your debut,
so isn't that enough?

77
00:07:46,809 --> 00:07:49,359
What more is there? Oh, I see.

78
00:07:49,359 --> 00:07:51,623
Want me to sleep with you?

79
00:08:02,345 --> 00:08:04,852
[Thai pop star Khun rumored to
debut in Korea through PNJS]

80
00:08:04,852 --> 00:08:07,425
I knew this would happen.
The CEO is soft on Khun.

81
00:08:07,425 --> 00:08:08,923
You can say that again.

82
00:08:08,923 --> 00:08:11,756
It's always us hard-working trainees
who take the brunt of it.

83
00:08:11,756 --> 00:08:15,036
They're going to kick one of us out, right?

84
00:08:15,036 --> 00:08:16,729
Who would it be?

85
00:08:16,729 --> 00:08:19,649
Hey. Of course it's going to be Shin Jae Min.

86
00:08:19,649 --> 00:08:22,921
He keeps drooling at guys like a dog.

87
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,561
Did you like it?

88
00:08:25,561 --> 00:08:27,934
You enjoyed it, didn't you?

89
00:08:29,124 --> 00:08:30,677
You think?

90
00:08:34,477 --> 00:08:35,977
What's up?

91
00:08:35,977 --> 00:08:38,844
Oh, hey. Did you see this?

92
00:08:46,757 --> 00:08:51,177
How could you let the article go up
before we even reached an agreement?

93
00:08:51,177 --> 00:08:52,964
I apologize.

94
00:08:52,964 --> 00:08:56,217
But the article didn't come from our side.

95
00:08:56,217 --> 00:09:00,044
The reporters wrote it on their own,
without checking with us first.

96
00:09:00,044 --> 00:09:04,064
This is a matter of trust
within our two companies.

97
00:09:04,064 --> 00:09:06,130
Jeez, we're sorry, okay?

98
00:09:06,130 --> 00:09:09,057
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

99
00:09:09,057 --> 00:09:13,770
Reporters nowadays don't even try
to cross-check before publishing a story.

100
00:09:13,770 --> 00:09:17,355
But we know better than to let something
so trivial pull us apart, right?

101
00:09:18,104 --> 00:09:22,877
If this is how things are handled,
we can't do business.

102
00:09:22,877 --> 00:09:26,724
The artist's opinion is what matters now.

103
00:09:27,430 --> 00:09:30,397
Well, Khun? Care to share your thoughts?

104
00:09:56,357 --> 00:10:01,114
[Jae Min, we need to work on our group project]

105
00:10:01,114 --> 00:10:04,782
[Where do you want to meet?]

106
00:10:31,985 --> 00:10:33,152
Khun!

107
00:10:33,152 --> 00:10:35,055
Stella!

108
00:10:38,685 --> 00:10:42,232
How did you even get here?
You didn't tell me you were coming.

109
00:10:42,232 --> 00:10:45,270
Of course I should be by your side.

110
00:10:49,205 --> 00:10:52,038
You seem to be doing great.

111
00:10:52,892 --> 00:10:55,632
I'm sorry I wasn't in touch.

112
00:10:55,632 --> 00:10:57,979
No, it's fine.

113
00:10:57,979 --> 00:11:00,785
It's good to see you doing well.

114
00:11:00,785 --> 00:11:04,259
So, are you going to invite me in?

115
00:11:04,259 --> 00:11:06,024
Come in.

116
00:11:33,825 --> 00:11:34,857
Khun!

117
00:11:34,857 --> 00:11:36,608
Stella!

118
00:11:37,912 --> 00:11:39,539
I'm jealous of Hyun Jae.

119
00:11:39,539 --> 00:11:41,859
Hey, if you're so jealous,
step up and debut already.

120
00:11:41,859 --> 00:11:43,892
You keep getting it wrong!

121
00:11:43,892 --> 00:11:45,465
I'm sorry, sir.

122
00:11:45,465 --> 00:11:47,985
What a massive jerk.

123
00:11:49,052 --> 00:11:51,079
Why do you work so hard?

124
00:11:51,079 --> 00:11:53,005
Because I want to do it...

125
00:11:53,005 --> 00:11:54,158
with you.

126
00:11:54,158 --> 00:11:55,774
Jae Min.

127
00:11:56,678 --> 00:11:58,938
I want you to meet someone.

